WEBVTT

00:03:29.333 --> 00:03:31.594
kama hii picha na Kumi Yamashita.

00:03:32.388 --> 00:03:34.406
Nawauliza kusogea karibu,

00:03:34.430 --> 00:03:36.651
na karibu zaidi,

00:03:36.675 --> 00:03:38.912
na wakati wakiangalia kazi ya sanaa,

00:03:38.936 --> 00:03:41.636
wanahitaji kuuliza maswali
kuhusu wanachoona.

00:03:42.341 --> 00:03:44.083
Na kama watauliza swali sahihi,

00:03:44.107 --> 00:03:45.725
kama, "Hii ni kazi gani ya sanaa?

00:03:45.749 --> 00:03:47.524
Ni mchoro? Ni sanamu?

00:03:47.548 --> 00:03:48.698
Imetengenezwa na nini?" ...

00:03:48.722 --> 00:03:51.951
watatambua kwamba hii kazi
nzima ya sanaa

00:03:51.975 --> 00:03:53.719
imetengenezwa na ubao wa mbao,

00:03:53.743 --> 00:03:55.372
misumari 10,000

00:03:55.396 --> 00:03:58.002
na kipande kizima cha kamba ya kushonea.

00:03:58.663 --> 00:04:00.841
Sasa hii inaweza vutia baadhi yenu,